{"tid":1890014,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩好好食嘅黃店早餐？","createTime":"2020-02-21T02:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T18:23:41.000Z","uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2e5eb507e59f58c1e4d57dceadd80f44b46e68","tid":1890014,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:46:10.000Z","msg":"小妹約咗男朋友聽日食早餐<br />\n大概想飲茶或者cafe <br />\n但其他類別嘅早餐都無問題，只要間嘢係黃<br />\n<br />\n地區不限，唔好太偏遠就得<br />\n（如元朗天水圍屯門及離島）<br />\n已知：老馮茶居、富東閣<br />\n想搵多幾間比男朋友揀<br />\n<br />\n請問大家有咩推薦？<br />\nThx"},{"pid":"2c465b1a0afb03ed7f87c2abefb2baa0c749a81c","tid":1890014,"uid":133525,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:49:08.000Z","msg":"大快活"},{"pid":"7d0b4897cf1c7acda07d5353ad0b888e3e907b28","tid":1890014,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"另外想問，旺角桔梗係咪24小時營業？<br />\n點解唔同嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFfAtZY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnFfAtZY.png&h=f0132139&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/054mpyj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F054mpyj.png&h=feae3c6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cef8c530f66f84b5470f026bf275b2d59e154f5d","tid":1890014,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:00:13.000Z","msg":"大家樂"},{"pid":"89c3c3864d04ed1f2778919c7b678eb16521e2ea","tid":1890014,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:17:04.000Z","msg":"時代冰室"},{"pid":"a6f0f034b8f0e8e0675aab6324678e7eb7a98fb5","tid":1890014,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"時代囉  <br />\n<br />\n100%fc左黃"},{"pid":"240babf87a1b0985de7b369747f9bae1ce0f4ed3","tid":1890014,"uid":2611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s